      "content": "it's just not that simple though. journaling doesn't change the fact that the person in those photos had a soul and a future, and i don't have either of those things anymore. i'm just tired of pretending to be a person when i feel like a hollow imitation. it's like i'm just occupying space that doesn't belong to me anymore.",
